{"title": "Atl\u00e0ntida", "description": "L'Atl\u00e0ntida \u00e9s un poema \u00e8pic que en el seu moment es consider\u00e0 com la culminaci\u00f3 de la recuperaci\u00f3 de la llengua catalana com a llengua liter\u00e0ria. Segueix la hist\u00f2ria d'un mariner genov\u00e8s que se salva d'un naufragi i comen\u00e7a a recollir antigues hist\u00f2ries de mariners, des del vell mite d'H\u00e8racles al Pirineu incendiat, passant pel continent de l'Atl\u00e0ntida i el seu enfosament, fins a la creaci\u00f3 del Mar Mediterrani i les seves cultures. // \"Atlantis\" is an epic poem that at the time was considered the culmination of the recovery of the Catalan language as a literary language. It follows the story of a Genoese sailor who survives a shipwreck and begins to collect ancient stories from sailors, from the old myth of Heracles in the burning Pyrenees, through the continent of Atlantis and its sinking, to the creation of the Mediterranean Sea and its cultures. (Summary by Joan Pujolar)", "duration": 10413, "language": "Catalan", "authors": [{"id": "16384", "name": "Jacint Verdaguer i Santal\u00f3"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/atlantida_2305_librivox/latlantida_2305.jpg", "copyright_year": "1878", "genres": ["Epics"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "Corda Jungfrau"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "jpujolar"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Kazbek"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "llunaemporda"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Introducci\u00f3", "readers": [18258], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/atlantida_2305_librivox/atlantida_01_verdaguer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 550}, {"section": 2, "title": "Cant primer: L'incendi dels Pirineus", "readers": [18258], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/atlantida_2305_librivox/atlantida_02_verdaguer_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1214}, {"section": 3, "title": "Cant segon: L'hort de les Hesp\u00e8rides", "readers": [18258], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/at